4 SYNOPSIS:
5 This bill would recreate the Alabama Commission
6 on the Evaluation of Services as a legislative
7 department and substantially revise provisions
8 governing the operation of the commission.
9 This bill would provide for the appointment of
10 the director of the commission and revise and clarify
11 certain duties of the commission.
12 This bill would also establish the Legislative
13 Committee on the Evaluation of Services to supervise
14 and control the commission.
15
16
17 A BILL
18 TO BE ENTITLED
19 AN ACT
20
21 Regarding the Alabama Commission on the Evaluation of
22 Services; to add Chapter 2B to Title 29, Code of Alabama 1975,
23 to recreate the commission as a legislative department; to
24 substantially revise the provisions governing the operation of
25 the commission; to provide for the appointment of a director;
26 to revise and clarify duties of the commission; to create the
27 Legislative Committee on the Evaluation of Services; to repeal
28 Chapter 2A, Title 29, Code of Alabama 1975, the existing law
